channel.title: Someone who's knows what they're doing please
channel.description: I need help. And everyone says the same thing. So i need someone to help me MORE than what everyone says because i've done it all. So i wana get my server to work. I compile it, run it, and it works for JUST ME. on 0.0.0.0... I have No-Ip and i have it going to my IP and i dont even have a firewall. So can someone tell me what else could it be thats making my server not work for other people besides myself?
